      published between April 2000 and June 2001. The new information summarized here
      includes: the discovery of the association of the NOD2 gene with Crohn's disease;
      the role of bacteria and the modulating effects of probiotics; the inverse
      association of appendectomy and ulcerative colitis; progress in imaging based on 
